{"tid":255452,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得遮既設計係一個失敗設計？","createTime":"2017-05-24T01:34:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-24T01:39:45.000Z","uid":117628,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"77e26442c535571232c2e04775135360df49adfe","tid":255452,"uid":117628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T01:34:33.000Z","msg":"首先，遮係覆蓋面積係一個圓形，但遮下面既人通常唔能夠企係圓形既中心，導致有時前面乾但背脊/書包濕哂，又或者一邊衫袖乾但另一邊衫袖濕哂<br />\n<br />\n其次，雨水通常唔係垂直咁落，而係打斜咁落，導致褲腳同鞋通常都濕哂<br />\n<br />\n結論：遮真係一個好失敗既設計"},{"pid":"76479196e6b905dd16df762b85a15460fce1c860","tid":255452,"uid":39701,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T01:36:55.000Z","msg":"咁你有咩高見"},{"pid":"1613a1b522488fd2bed433b02dbc53fc9d44a6f0","tid":255452,"uid":35639,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T01:38:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/24/093816_5af249d6d0c646f40305d7680d3ee8ac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F24%2F093816_5af249d6d0c646f40305d7680d3ee8ac.jpg&h=6ec48a71&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5a73c9cf125631e7b3a41f51bef1f46c8e9b69ad","tid":255452,"uid":18118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T01:38:21.000Z","msg":"之前梁洛施套蟲不知有把遮係遮晒全身 點解一直冇人大量生產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"537e95fb1e1bb3f68ebe9be1735d355ec6075d46","tid":255452,"uid":18118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T01:38:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/24/093816_5af249d6d0c646f40305d7680d3ee8ac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F24%2F093816_5af249d6d0c646f40305d7680d3ee8ac.jpg&h=6ec48a71&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>